subject: Meeting Rescheduled
body: Dear John, I hope this message finds you well. I wanted to inform you that due to unforeseen circumstances, our meeting originally scheduled for this Wednesday has been rescheduled to next Friday at 10 AM. I apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and hope the new time works for you. Please let me know if you have any conflicts with the rescheduled time. Looking forward to our meeting. Best regards, Jane.

subject: Your Order Has Shipped
body: Dear John, We are excited to inform you that your order #12345 has been successfully processed and shipped. Your package is on its way and should arrive at your doorstep within the next 3-5 business days. You can track your package's progress online using the tracking number provided in your shipping confirmation email. We hope you are looking forward to receiving your order as much as we enjoyed preparing it for you. Thank you for choosing Acme Corp. Best regards, The Acme Corp Support Team.
